node.text: Can't believe it's been almost a year since we released our second book...and hosted our first ever virtual book tour! 🎂✨ If you bought a copy of The Home Edit Life, we hope you loved reading it...or just looking at the pictures, both count! Our goal for writing this follow-up book was to help y'all dig into the contents that make up your life. In other words, organizing for how you really live, and kicking guilt to the curb! 🌈✨
